Tafseer (commentary)
--------------------

The tafseer used by this project is التفسير الميسر (Al-Muyassar), the concise
tafseer issued by the King Fahd Complex for the Printing of the Holy Quran
(مجمع الملك فهد لطباعة المصحف الشريف). It was downloaded with
`pnpm data:fetch:tafseer` from the AlQuran.cloud API (edition "ar.muyassar")
and is stored, unchanged, at:

    prisma/data/tafseer-muyassar.json

