Recitation audio
----------------

The daily ayah's optional recitation audio is the standard Mushaf Murattal
recordings of the reciters listed in src/database/reference/reciters.ts
(among them Mahmoud Khalil Al-Husary, Mohamed Siddiq Al-Minshawi, Abdul Basit
Abdul Samad, Mishary Rashid Alafasy, Maher Al-Muaiqly, and Saad Al-Ghamdi). The
audio is fetched per ayah from everyayah.com and is NOT stored or redistributed
in this repository; only the URLs are referenced, and Telegram caches each clip
after the first send. Each recording remains the work and property of its
reciter and original publisher, used here for non-commercial educational
purposes (helping people learn and memorize the Quran). No audio is modified.

